m_DisplayNameText.LocalisedValue: Whenever this holy dwarven urgrosh lands a hit but doesn't deal any {g|Encyclopedia:Physical_Damage}physical damage{/g}, the next hit deals force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} instead of the normal {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Type}piercing{/g} or slashing weapon damage.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: Whenever this holy dwarven urgrosh lands a hit but doesn't deal any {g|Encyclopedia:Physical_Damage}physical damage{/g}, the next hit deals force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} instead of the normal {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Type}piercing{/g} or slashing weapon damage.
This is a +1 cold iron ghost touch weapon.

This is a +3 brilliant energy heartseeker weapon. This weapon can tear the soul of a living enemy: whenever it lands a hit, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d6{/g} force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This weapon was once the seat of Finnean's soul. Now that the soul of the Sarkorian Pathfinder has left the weapon, it has fallen silent forever.
